        },
        {
          "text": "**After 12 years:** son is $x + 12$, father is $3x + 12$."
        },
        {
          "text": "**Equation** (father is twice son):"
        },
        {
          "math": "3x + 12 = 2(x + 12) = 2x + 24"
        },
        {
          "math": "x = 12"
        }
      ],
      "difficulty": "medium"
