          "text": "**Five years ago:** sister was $x - 5$, Tara was $2x - 5$."
        },
        {
          "text": "**Equation:**"
        },
        {
          "math": "(x - 5) + (2x - 5) = 11"
        },
        {
          "math": "3x - 10 = 11 \\;\\Longrightarrow\\; x = 7"
